{"word":"H1973 - הָלְאָה - hâlᵉʼâh - haw-leh-aw' - Back","slug":"H1973","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">הָלְאָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hâlᵉʼâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>haw-leh-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Back"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D4;&#x05DC;&#x05D0;&#x05D4; - ha&#x0302;l<sup>e</sup>'a&#x0302;h</b> - <i>haw-leh-aw'</i><p/>From the primitive form of the article; <i>to the distance</i>, that is, <i>far away</i>; also (of time) <i>thus far: - </i>back, beyond, (hence-) forward, hitherto, thenceforth, yonder."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1972\">H1972</a>"}]}